RACE_LEAP_OF_FAITH_V1 CREATED BY WANNAFUCK You'll discover why I gave the map that name when you play it for the first time :) It's not an easy map and some racers will eventually die before finishing the map. Go pro racers!
Map info: - Medium size! - 23 spawn points - 1 lap - Sun - Light Environment - HDR - 2 "houses" where you can spare some time - 11 Checkpoints - 3 Ready Zones
----------------------------------- In order to play this map, you need Rally Race Mod installed in your server. If you want to play this map, you can join FRAGXL.com | Rally RaceMania - 80.172.230.146:27015
